    "id": "v22"
  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng ta n\xE9n gi\u1EADn. Ta h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy v\xEC danh ta \u0111\u1EC3 danh \u0111\xF3 kh\xF4ng b\u1ECB xem th\u01B0\u1EDDng gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c d\xE2n \u0111ang ch\u1EE9ng ki\u1EBFn khi ta mang d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en ra kh\u1ECFi Ai-c\u1EADp. "), mdx("h6", {
