  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Ta h\u1ECFi ch\xFAng: '\u0110\u1ED3i cao n\u1EA7y m\xE0 c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EBFn th\u1EDD ph\u1EE5ng l\xE0 g\xEC?' Ng\xE0y nay ch\u1ED7 \u0111\xF3 v\u1EABn g\u1ECDi l\xE0 \u0110\u1ED3i Cao. "), mdx("h6", {
