  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD mang c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i ra kh\u1ECFi c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc ngo\u1EA1i qu\u1ED1c. Ta s\u1EBD d\xF9ng quy\u1EC1n n\u0103ng l\u1EDBn lao, s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh v\xE0 c\u01A1n th\u1ECBnh n\u1ED9 ta \u0111\u1EC3 gom c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\u1EA1i t\u1EEB c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc m\xE0 c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB ph\xE2n t\xE1n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD mang c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i ra n\u01A1i sa m\u1EA1c kh\xF4ng d\xE2n \u1EDF. N\u01A1i \u0111\xF3 ta s\u1EBD ph\xE2n x\u1EED c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i m\u1EB7t \u0111\u1ED1i m\u1EB7t. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i nh\u01B0 ta \u0111\xE3 tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i trong sa m\u1EA1c c\u1EE7a x\u1EE9 Ai-c\u1EADp, CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EBFm c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i nh\u01B0 chi\xEAn v\xE0 s\u1EBD mang c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0o trong giao \u01B0\u1EDBc ta. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v38"
  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD di\u1EC7t h\u1EBFt nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB kh\xF4ng v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi ta hay ch\u1ED1ng ngh\u1ECBch ta. Ta s\u1EBD mang ch\xFAng ra kh\u1ECFi x\u1EE9 hi\u1EC7n \u0111ang s\u1ED1ng nh\u01B0ng ch\xFAng s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c v\xE0o x\u1EE9 \xCDt-ra-en. R\u1ED3i c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt ta l\xE0 CH\xDAA.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v39"
  }, "v39"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ph\xE1n: \"H\u1EE1i d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en, h\xE3y \u0111i th\u1EDD th\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111i. Nh\u01B0ng sau n\u1EA7y c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD nghe ta; c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\xF2n khinh th\u01B0\u1EDDng danh th\xE1nh c\u1EE7a ta b\u1EB1ng c\xE1c c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 v\xE0 t\xE0 th\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a m\xECnh n\u1EEFa. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v40"
  }, "v40"), mdx("p", null, "Tr\xEAn n\xFAi th\xE1nh ta, n\xFAi cao c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en, to\xE0n d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en s\u1EBD ph\u1EE5c v\u1EE5 ta trong x\u1EE9, CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. Ta s\u1EBD ch\u1EA5p nh\u1EADn c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u1EDF \u0111\xF3. Ta s\u1EBD ch\u1EDD \u0111\u1EE3i c\xE1c c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i, c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 \u0111\u1EA7u m\xF9a g\u1EB7t v\xE0 c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 th\xE1nh c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. "), mdx("h6", {
