    "id": "v42"
  }, "v42"), mdx("p", null, "Khi ta mang c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0o x\u1EE9 \xCDt-ra-en, x\u1EE9 m\xE0 ta \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a c\xF9ng t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i th\xEC c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng ta l\xE0 CH\xDAA. "), mdx("h6", {
