    "id": "v44"
  }, "v44"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD \u0111\u1ED1i x\u1EED v\u1EDBi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xEC danh th\xE1nh ta, ch\u1EB3ng ph\u1EA3i v\xEC nh\u1EEFng h\xE0nh vi \xE1c \u0111\u1ED9c hay vi\u1EC7c l\xE0m d\u01A1 b\u1EA9n c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. R\u1ED3i c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD bi\u1EBFt ta l\xE0 CH\xDAA, h\u1EE1i d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en. CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ph\xE1n v\u1EADy.\"Ba-by-l\xF4n l\xE0 g\u01B0\u01A1m c\u1EE7a Ch\xFAa "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v45"
  }, "v45"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA ph\xE1n c\xF9ng t\xF4i r\u1EB1ng: "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v46"
  }, "v46"), mdx("p", null, "\"H\u1EE1i con ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, h\xE3y nh\xECn v\u1EC1 ph\xEDa Nam. H\xE3y n\xF3i ti\xEAn tri ngh\u1ECBch c\xF9ng ph\u01B0\u01A1ng Nam v\xE0 khu r\u1EEBng N\xEA-gh\xE9p . "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v47"
  }, "v47"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y n\xF3i c\xF9ng r\u1EEBng r\u1EB1ng: 'H\xE3y nghe l\u1EDDi CH\xDAA. CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ph\xE1n: Ta s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng ch\xE2m l\u1EEDa \u0111\u1ED1t ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xE0 ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t m\u1ECDi c\xE2y xanh v\xE0 c\xE2y kh\xF4 c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u01A1i. S\u1EBD kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 n\xE0o d\u1EADp t\u1EAFt \u0111\xE1m l\u1EEDa \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. M\u1ECDi ph\xEDa t\u1EEB Nam \u0111\u1EBFn B\u1EAFc s\u1EBD c\u1EA3m bi\u1EBFt s\u1EE9c n\xF3ng c\u1EE7a n\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v48"
  }, "v48"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD th\u1EA5y r\u1EB1ng ta, CH\xDAA, \u0111\xE3 ch\xE2m l\u1EEDa \u0111\xF3. Kh\xF4ng ai d\u1EADp t\u1EAFt \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c.'\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v49"
  }, "v49"), mdx("p", null, "R\u1ED3i t\xF4i th\u01B0a, \"\xD4i, CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF! D\xE2n ch\xFAng n\xF3i v\u1EC1 t\xF4i r\u1EB1ng, '\xD4ng ta ch\u1EC9 k\u1EC3 chuy\u1EC7n b\u1ECBa \u0111\u1EB7t \u0111\xF3 th\xF4i.'\""), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
